00:10:03.510 --> 00:10:05.010
Merci de ne pas intervenir !

00:10:05.760 --> 00:10:07.980
Vous l'avez entendue ? Partez devant.

00:10:09.690 --> 00:10:10.610
Allons-y.

00:10:12.770 --> 00:10:16.120
