00:12:49.640 --> 00:12:51.110
C'est la fin du voyage.

00:12:57.190 --> 00:12:57.770
Va-t'en !

00:13:16.710 --> 00:13:17.720
Feu !

00:13:23.290 --> 00:13:24.720
